{"tid":2082943,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大就愈唔想食放題","createTime":"2020-06-28T12:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T12:53:43.000Z","uid":104138,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4885f82bced7341857022334a183b2e5aefa7e","tid":2082943,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"以前讀緊書果陣，放題係一個幾新鮮既概念<br />\n想像唔到比兩舊幾水可以係咁叫野食野飲同甜品<br />\n款式又多過一般自助餐又唔駛要比成 4舊幾去酒店食<br />\n叫完野食就有人送來，唔駛自己去拎<br />\n記得第一次食果陣仲食到上到巴士後想嘔埋出來<br />\n但畢業後見識多左已經接受唔到放題既垃圾質素，食量都無以前咁大<br />\n寧願逐碟叫，但每碟都高質，貴d都願意比<br />\n放題真係比錢買難受"},{"pid":"7ad5978b107a771526007b3ed6be6645277633e8","tid":2082943,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"窮撚先食放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82368982ea5ed7c5979c7f9829968025e7c3a438","tid":2082943,"uid":347965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4a4a846d04e9d7b914f6846973d0b67e96c6d9b5","tid":2082943,"uid":3987,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"香港嘅放題根本係個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fea677d147c005272a63a1234770a0fa1a7207","tid":2082943,"uid":41394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"出黎做野已經無再食，又多人又嘈"},{"pid":"fda739f08945d26a53f1222bf5077b62d8fabf3b","tid":2082943,"uid":301923,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"如果百幾蚊既放題就會食下<br />\n都係食到點到即止就算<br />\n依家寧願食貴啲 逐碟叫仲好<br />\n唔明啲人食到嘔係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前世係唔係乞兒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cad20cae85ba49282c5ebea9bdb42cdc28cc005","tid":2082943,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"我淨係知有間連鎖放題係撐警藍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d743130412cb9b6e02df44ad243a805b08d3537","tid":2082943,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"由細到大都唔鐘意放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe3fa4b9669acc635afd8c7bbae137374dc448d","tid":2082943,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"鐘意自己煮多d  食材比想像中平<br />\n<br />\n以前唔識野 以為食材同茶記一樣咁貴 <br />\n<br />\n50蚊先得少少扒 <br />\n<br />\n利申 絲打"},{"pid":"dfbb4e9ee999e5c3b74aa60593196a6b682fdb1e","tid":2082943,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ad5978b107a771526007b3ed6be6645277633e8","tid":2082943,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"窮撚先食放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"呢句真，放題入面d 食客既食相真係好難睇，好似千語千尋入面d豬咁<br />\n當然有小部分人純料因為gathering 被迫食放題"},{"pid":"37dec489b9cae943da24423064fe8163d46026bf","tid":2082943,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"有啲放題係唔差嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />質素okay<br />\n不過人老左食唔落咁多 不如食散嗌嘅 精緻啲"},{"pid":"848a5403b3e4230829c9976b822a518f83dcf7b6","tid":2082943,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"大部份都好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bd11e21b7fe95e3631083af9b894ab99ac7b97","tid":2082943,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"你以為你食得夠多就叫回本<br />\n其實你愈食愈蝕"},{"pid":